My first publication for skyrim
it was very hard for me to understand all the questions before uploading ...
sorry if I choose the wrong categories...
I think that might be only a help for mod creators
to find a possibility to get in or out of a cave,area etc
check out to use it for your mod
I think there are too many magic-doors,portals etc...
my intention is to support other mod creators by my assistance ... specially those sections
so...feel free to ask
excuse me if I'm wrong with my idea
